WEBVTT

18:44.960 --> 18:46.550 line:80%
I'll take what you just said

18:46.870 --> 18:48.040 line:80%
as mere words spoken in anger.

18:48.040 --> 18:49.150 line:80%
I won't take them to heart.

18:49.150 --> 18:49.720 line:80%
Don't.

18:50.800 --> 18:52.550 line:80%
You must take them to heart.

18:53.070 --> 18:55.730 line:80%
And there's no need
to speak of being my brother.
